Package: owntone
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, avahi-daemon
Suggests: sqlite3, libavcodec-extra
Description: Serves your local music library and Spotify library to AirPlay,
 Chromecast and Roku speakers, as well iTunes (DAAP) and MPD compatible clients.
 You can control OwnTone with Apple Remote (and DACP compatibles), with an MPD
 client or with the built-in web interface at http://localhost:3689/.
 .
 This package is specifically made for Raspberry Pi OS. OwnTone was previously
 called forked-daapd.

